---
---

<section class="problem section" id="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">The real problem</p>
    <h2>Planners remind you on a schedule. Your brain doesn't run on one.</h2>
    <div class="problem__grid">
      <article class="problem__card">
        <h3>Hyperfocus hits</h3>
        <p>Reminders fire at 9am while you're deep in flow. You can't act — but the app already marked you "late."</p>
      </article>
      <article class="problem__card">
        <h3>Midnight erasure</h3>
        <p>Tasks vanish at midnight instead of waiting patiently. Missed once, gone forever — and the guilt sticks.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="problem__card">
        <h3>Red badges</h3>
        <p>Overdue counters and streaks feel punishing, not supportive. ADHD brains need delivery, not discipline theater.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem {
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border-block: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .problem h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    max-width: 22ch;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .problem__grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
  }

  .problem__card {
    padding: 1.75rem;
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .problem__card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .problem__card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
  }
</style>
